{"tid":2515021,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★全港177公頃潛在套丁土地儲備　料建逾7萬公屋單位","createTime":"2021-05-03T15:45:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T15:48:24.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d211ce34d1976df25a80ca9027f2826b5622dd8f","tid":2515021,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T15:45:53.000Z","msg":"政府若剔除上述約177公頃的潛在套丁土儲當中涉及的魚塘、濕地、農地，將剩餘約149公頃土地。根據規劃署的《香港規劃標準與準則》，以「鄉郊住宅發展密度第一區」最高密度發展，團體認為，如將該149公頃的潛在套丁土儲皆興建鄉村式公屋，以<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>單位面積約700平方呎計算，則能提供多達7.45萬個公營房屋單位</strong></span>，滿足逾22萬人的住屋需求。相反，若用以興建丁屋，按目前的分割地段情況估算，估計每公頃只能提供40間丁屋。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20210503/bkn-20210503130630156-0503_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20210503%2Fbkn-20210503130630156-0503_00822_001.html&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnrHKdwoo7KeUephkEgg9e70%3D&h=40657f57\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20210503/bkn-20210503130630156-0503_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"f235fe8dd09ccafa45cf144a50e4408dc649bce9","tid":2515021,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T15:46:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02528d0231b1c957d8ea1394e8ebaba164ae48e3","tid":2515021,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T15:47:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVx1YSjaswGxMDHUzzYNSoSEWN58V89UfyuM4U36T8D5Y?filename=K38OEe7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK38OEe7.gif&h=3ea487d5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0009504ba1aac4f7a45ab1ecc6b7cdaae0c11c20","tid":251